    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Provinces outside the borders of, but under the jurisdiction and sovereignty of a primary political entity, such as a nation or empire. A historical example was Portugal's Overseas Province of Angola.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
